```
1. Create Project
   └─> "NC1 Stage 1 Tune"

2. Add ROMs
   ├─> "Stock" (baseline)
   └─> "Working Tune" (current)

3. Edit Tables
   └─> App auto-tracks changes
       └─> Optional: add comment "Richened WOT for safety"

4. View History
